#message:16:020
{
	[Next]
	Do you know of Yokubou no Naizou?[BR]
	[Pause 15]It was originally a sanctum of[BR]
	respect for the Chinese.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	However, the Japanese vandalized it[BR]
	and it's now a tomb of misconstrued[BR]
	and confusing feelings.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I've heard, even now, there is a[BR]
	madman trying to ressurect the[BR]
	ancient daemon that sleeps beneath[BR]
	that crypt.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[SaveColor][Color:04]Xin Suì[RestoreColor] is its name and only those[BR]
	with a twisted heart wish to dream[BR]
	of reviving it.[BR]
