}

#message:16:021
{
	[Next]
	As you may or may not know,[BR]
	Bower is the God of Unity and[BR]
	he inherits many ill powers.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Strangely, his brother does not[BR]
	inherit any of the powers he does.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Not much is known about Bower's[BR]
	family, besides his grandmother.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	What I [Wave]CAN[/fx] tell you though is that[BR]
	Bower's brother actually has a name.[BR]
	[Pause 20]Go on. Take a wild guess what his[BR]
	brother's name is.[BR]
